title: Counter-Strike 1.6 SteelSeries WarZone 2017
description: Counter-Strike 1.6 SteelSeries , play Counter-Strike 1.6 in another experience ! Now you can play in another experience and with a highly FPS ! The gameplay wasn't modified , all is based on the clasic CS 1.6 ! There was much optimized things which will help you to play at the better experience ! Few things which was added on this version : # A guard which will verify all servers activity [ If one is trying to modify your game client , the guard will block it ] # A list of servers updated weekly ! # Now all your configurations will be saved # New skins for a HIGH FPS and on the worst PC # The client kit works on all multiplayer server [ which have the protocol 47/48 ] # Includes the latest bots # The archive max. size is 230 [ more less then other clients ] NOTE : To run the game , you can use one of the launchers which i offered to you : - Counter-Strike 1.6.exe [ The principal executable ] - Counter-Strike 1.6.vbs [ Another executable file based on Virtual Basic programming language ] - Counter-Strike 1.6.bat [ Another executable file based on Batch programming language ] Thanks for downloading the file :) Here are few snapshots : http://cs16-go.ru/_ld/0/86277019.jpg http://cs16-go.ru/_ld/0/17119374.jpg http://cs16-go.ru/_ld/0/94931743.jpg http://cs16-go.ru/_ld/0/76704241.jpg
